e-1606185981123" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1606185981123"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><b style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;"><br></b></p><p><b>What is your health + wellness routine?</b></p><p><b><br></b></p></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1606179812183" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1606179812183"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Here’s an average day of healthy daily habits/my routine:&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>Wake up, drink a full glass of water to get into the habit of drinking water throughout the day, non-toxic skincare routine, coffee while I journal what I am grateful for and write down my to do list for the day, a FFM workout, nourishing meals throughout the day (full of veggies, fruit, protein, fiber, healthy fat, unrefined carbs and I definitely leave room for treats), an afternoon walk outside for a work break, time with family and friends, dessert, skincare then sleep :) I usually get 8 hours of sleep per night.&nbsp;</p></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1606186020155" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1606186020155"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><b style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;"><br></b></p><p><b>What is it like to use social media as a platform for your business? Do you have any advice, tips or expertise for anyone who is trying to do the same?&nbsp;</b></p><p><b><br></b></p></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1606186003307" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1606186003307"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>I love love love posting on Insta and interacting with the community! I don’t plan my posts ahead of time, I just share what I feel each day and genuinely get excited to post/story. My advice would be to be yourself, don’t focus so much on gaining followers (rather, serve the ones you have well), provide VALUE, and share what you’re passionate about!!</p></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1606186621612" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1606186621612"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><br></p></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1606189307904" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1606189307904"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><b>Where you can our audience find you?</b></p><p><br></p></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1606186894076" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1606186894076"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>You can find me on Instagram @fitformebycourtney and my program Fit For Me by Courtney at Fitformebycourtney.com.</p></div></div><!--gfsplit--></div><div id="divContentBk"></div><!--End_Gem_Page_Main_Editor-->
